{
  "stem": "23730.3",
  "chunk_idx": 10,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 6.6,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 62,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "In Wustegiersdorf, we got half-- half a slice of bread, a little margarine, and in the evening when we came home from work, a plate of soup.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Non-existent.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I mean, we had to use pails, a pail, right?",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there were-- there were turns.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "You had to take your turn that when the pail was full up, you had to carry-- carry down the pail three floors and empty the pail and go  back, right?",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 63,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "That was-- that-- and for your turn, for an hour you had to watch the pail.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 64,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I would say around 10 months, between 9 and 10 months.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Conditions improved.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They did improve, first-- especially for me, who ended up in that workshop, that I was-- I was protected from the last winter of the war, which was pretty hard, because we had no adequate clothing for the winter.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And there was extra food from Anton, right?",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And you felt a little-- again, you're a  mensch.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Under Anton, you felt you are a mensch really truly.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "That was the real Schindler, because Schindler didn't do it really out of goodness, let's say.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 65,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "We don't know.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "But that man Anton out of sheer goodness and [NON-ENGLISH], of human feelings that little man Anton.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Never asked his second name.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Why would I ask his second name?",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "Anton is Anton finish.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 66,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "But how can you-- how can you thank you when everything is over if you don't know the name?",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "That's my greatest regret, not only for Anton, because there were other people who helped.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Oh, yes, there were other people who showed some human feelings.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 67,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Oh, yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "You see, the Russian Army, the Red Army, were advancing from the east.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We could hear the bombardment already.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 68,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So the-- the camp had to be evacuated.",
      "word_count": 8
    }
  ],
